  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine the feasibility of delivering different community nutritional interventions to
      chronic obstructive pulmonary disease (COPD) patients at moderate or severe risk of
      malnutrition following a hospitalisation for an acute exacerbation of COPD.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
